IF YOU DONT SEE ANY ERRORS SHOWING U HAVE NO ACCESS YOU ARE GOOD TO GO! Otherwise first find out maybe BCDEDIT DEBUG was not enabled
(its easy to check if it is enabled u will see mark on the right down corner of your screen at the desktop TestingMode)
9)In this list which U will get U need to find: PCI Express bridge and Videocard (here its 00:17.0 Bridge and 02:00.0 GPU)
10) U need this parameters to modify the registers.bat file and Check_current_registers.bat with your addresses for the bridge and GPU
11) after editing ure bat files run Check_current_registers.bat:
ECHO OFF
cd C:\bettercamp-main\fix9400M_EFI
PAUSE
setpci -s "00:17.0" 3e.b
PAUSE
setpci -s "02:00.0" 04.b
PAUSE
this will show you what is set right now!
it will be like numbers:
C:\bettercamp-main\fix9400M_EFI>setpci -s "02:00.0" 04.b
07
